00:38:14,090 --> 00:38:15,080
Yesterday night,

611
00:38:15,080 --> 00:38:17,120
Lord Baili, the Minister of Works was killed at the Baili Mansion.

612
00:38:17,120 --> 00:38:17,820
Baili Mansion.

613
00:38:17,820 --> 00:38:21,600
[The Intelligence Services: Lord Chu]

614
00:38:19,170 --> 00:38:20,850
Regarding the case that occured at the dock south to the capital,

615
00:38:20,850 --> 00:38:21,650
what happened there?

616
00:38:21,600 --> 00:38:24,120
[Agent of the Intelligence Services: Han Dongqing]

617
00:38:22,240 --> 00:38:23,100
The Grand Court

618
00:38:23,130 --> 00:38:24,760
said it was a dispute among the associations.

619
00:38:24,760 --> 00:38:25,520
Nonsense.

620
00:38:26,690 --> 00:38:28,170
I've asked someone to look into it.

621
00:38:28,170 --> 00:38:29,210
There was news that

622
00:38:29,210 --> 00:38:30,290
Gao Bingzhu appeared at

623
00:38:30,290 --> 00:38:31,950
the dock south of the capital.

624
00:38:32,850 --> 00:38:33,890
Gao Bingzhu.

625
00:38:35,130 --> 00:38:36,130
He must be related

626
00:38:36,280 --> 00:38:38,160
to the murder of the informer.

627
00:38:39,530 --> 00:38:41,120
We, the Intelligence Services,

628
00:38:41,120 --> 00:38:43,130
did not receive any news.

629
00:38:44,680 --> 00:38:46,730
We've known for a while that
there are spies in the Intelligence Services.

630
00:38:46,730 --> 00:38:48,530
This is what worries me the most.

631
00:38:48,920 --> 00:38:50,720
Do we report this to the empress?

632
00:38:53,610 --> 00:38:54,890
Outside the capital,

633
00:38:55,330 --> 00:38:58,050
seven people from the Unwelcome Well  were killed.

634
00:38:58,050 --> 00:38:59,150
Bring me the detailed files.

635
00:38:59,150 --> 00:39:00,790
[Buddha Dalü: Wang Zixuan, Born on the twenty-ninth of June, from Chang'an]

636
00:38:59,530 --> 00:39:00,060
Yes, sir.

637
00:39:04,950 --> 00:39:09,150
[Baili Mansion]

638
00:39:14,450 --> 00:39:15,050
Hongyi.

639
00:39:15,450 --> 00:39:17,180
You've not rested for two days.

640
00:39:17,440 --> 00:39:18,560
Your father

641
