00:39:29,800 --> 00:39:31,050
I'll try to persuade him.

648
00:39:31,050 --> 00:39:31,850
You leave too.

649
00:39:33,680 --> 00:39:35,540
I'll keep watch on my own tonight.

650
00:39:35,650 --> 00:39:36,250
Hongyi...

651
00:39:36,450 --> 00:39:37,310
Get out of here.

652
00:40:20,540 --> 00:40:28,360
[Baili Mansion]

653
00:40:39,640 --> 00:40:40,840
I knew you would come.

654
00:40:48,600 --> 00:40:51,060
Are you not reporting me to the authorities?

655
00:40:51,440 --> 00:40:52,240
It wasn't you.

656
00:40:54,320 --> 00:40:55,450
You're not the one

